summary: Book about female superheroes: And this was one of Wonder Woman's most feminist eras... and here's when the writers first...
body:
Book about female superheroes: And this was one of Wonder Woman’s most feminist eras… and here’s when the writers first suggested all the Amazons were gay…and in this issue Mystique had a female partner and they adopted a daughter…oh and did you know the first female Captain Marvel was black…

Me: oh yeah, let me jot that down, gotta keep notes for more…research….purely scientific reasons…

summary: For those that don’t remember The Dark Knight was absolutely huge. It had literally everything possible going for it. You...
caption:
For those that don’t remember The Dark Knight was absolutely huge. It had literally everything possible going for it. You couldn’t go five minutes without hearing how it was the best movie ever, the Joker was something everybody wanted to see. There was (and still is) an entire army of fanboys who sang it’s praises non stop
With Captain Marvel it was the opposite. People were curious about it but there was no “must see” moment. It was a prequel, there were no big hero names to give her back up. She had a cat and Fury. And there was no army of fanboys supporting her. It was the opposite in fact. There was a concentrated effort to bring her down.
And despite all of this it took her a mere month to surpass The Dark Knight. Nobody can stop our girl

summary: Summary: Y/n needs an outfit for her cosplay convention, luckily her girlfriend has a pretty cool suit Pairing: Carol Danvers x...
body:
Summary: Y/n needs an outfit for her cosplay convention, luckily her girlfriend has a pretty cool suit

Pairing: Carol Danvers x fem! reader

Warning: like one curse word, lots of fluff

A/n: My first Captain Marvel fic! This one’s pretty cute and Carol deserves more love. Requested by the lovely @freedomfighterposts, thank you for your request <3 Enjoy some gay shit

Y/n looked down at the suit she had made. She frowned. Something’s missing.

Y/n glanced over to the open wardrobe where Carol’s suit hang. 

No, I couldn’t possibly

~~~

Y/n strutted into the convention with pride. She knew she was the best dressed. People gawked at her as she walked by.

The suit fit her perfectly despite it being made for Carol. The moment she put it on it fit to her size.

“Hey dude, that suit it awesome!” a man dressed as Thor said. Y/n smiled and thanked him.

“Where’d you get it?” he asked looking at the suit in awe.

Y/n let out a breath, “I got it from my girlfriend.”

~~~

“Y/n?” Carol called into the house. She had come back from grocery shopping.

She looked into their shared room. “Hello?”

Y/n was no where in sight. She glanced over to the wardrobe.

A note was taped to the hanger where her suit used to be.

Carol,

I went to the convention with your suit, please don’t be mad. It is really cool and you never let me try it on before.

Hope we’re still together when I get back :),

your greatest love,

Y/n

Carol laughed at the note. 

“God I love that woman.”

~~~

Y/n tipped toed into the house in hopes of not waking her girlfriend. She went upstairs to their bedroom.

Carol was sat on the bed with her arms crossed and smirking.

“Carol, I can explain,” Y/n started. She sounded like a child that was just caught colouring the walls with marker.

 Carol tilted her head to the side and looked her lover up and down.

“I must say, you look quite sexy in it,” Carol stated in a low voice.

Y/n raised an eyebrow. “Oh really? Think I could save the world from some aliens?”

She put her hands on her hips posing like a superhero.

“C’mere my knight in shining armour!” Carol put her arms out for a hug. Y/n walked over to the bed and lay on top of her.

Y/n looked up at Carol.

“I love you,” Carol whispered gliding her hand threw Y/n’s hair.

Y/n simply smiled and pressed their lips together. The two leaned into each other.

Carol’s hands fell from Y/n hair to her back and began rubbing small circles. Y/n sighed into the kiss and made it deeper.

When they eventually broke apart Y/n looked up at her girlfriend with love in her eyes. 

“I love you more than anything,” she whispered. Carol smiled back at her and began removing the suit from Y/n’s body.

Y/n exhaled when it was off. “That suit is really fucking cool but damn is it tight.”

summary: Mar-Vell/dr. Wendy Lawson is such an interesting character.  There are so many questions like what made her realise the truth...
body:
Mar-Vell/dr. Wendy Lawson is such an interesting character. 

There are so many questions like what made her realise the truth about the Kree and the Skrull? What was her life before? Who did she leave behind on Hala? Maybe she had a family there? What kind of research did she do before? How did it benefit the Kree and how guilty does she feel because of it? How much combat did she take part in?
